title: Maysoon Zayid: On Finding Resilience and Laughter Amid Pain
description: In this encore episode, comedian, writer and disabilities advocate Maysoon Zayid tells WSJ's Veronica Dagher how the coronavirus has impacted those who perform for a living and how she's coping financially.
